description:
ANN highlights that Adventist Australian cyclists mobilize to raise funds for earthquake victims. 

This week, Digital Evangelism reaches and impacts many with the Gospel. Adventist GLOW Ministry impacts with tracts across the Trans-European region. ADRA assists victims of flooding in Haiti. Adventist message touches the hearts of thousands in India. 

Watch as ANN highlights these stories and reports on other news from around the world. 

For more Adventist news, subscribe to our YouTube channel. 

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church. For all things Adventist news, visit adventist.news.
